flightaware data.
I'll try to go for it again on Saturday. The weather isn't terrible right now, but it's only Monday.
The difficulties are already starting to appear. I'll probably have A LOT of trouble getting a medical certificate, due to the FAA's stance on certain medications.
Not impossible, but it will take ENORMOUS time and require A LOT of extra work.
Even though it's discouraging, it's just another problem to solve and, for now, it seems *completely* manageable. It's just that it will take a lot of time and $$$.
In case the challenge awaiting me interests you.
The FAA is not a fan of ADHD. They do not issue a medical certificate if one is undergoing treatment for it.
